# My Book Online

Welcome to your own personal publishing platform.

As an author you can go all the way from writing to creating a Kindle book for online sales.



MyBook gives you tools that you need to write your own book

## 1. Get a Big Idea

Decide on topic, title, and concept


## 2. Write Chapters

Draft out your ideas as chapters


## 4. Edit Content

Edit and refine each chapter over a period of time


## 5. Publish

Publish as website and Kindle book


---

MyBook provides guidance throughout each step of the writing process.  All you need to supply is creativity.